t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a671c94 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"a671c94\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Similar Superficial Pathology<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-8de6aae elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"8de6aae\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-c5f7f4c\" data-id=\"c5f7f4c\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9a6c25a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"9a6c25a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Erysipelas<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Infection Limited to the Outer Skin (Epidermis &amp; Superficial Dermis)<\/li><li>Presentation:<ul><li>Fiery Red Erythema<\/li><li>Pain<\/li><li><strong>Sharp Borders<\/strong> (Well Demarcated)<\/li><li>Develops More Rapidly than Cellulitis<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Most Common Organism: Group A Streptococcus<\/li><li>Treatment: Antibiotics<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Contact Dermatitis<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Definition: Localized Skin Inflammation Due to Chemical or Physical Agents<ul><li>Noninfectious<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Common Causes:<ul><li>Water<\/li><li>Detergents<\/li><li>Soaps<\/li><li>Oxidizing Agents (Bleach or Benzoyl Peroxide)<\/li><li>Metals<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Presentation:<ul><li>Erythema<\/li><li>Edema<\/li><li>Vesicles or Bullae<\/li><li>Pruritis or Burning \u2013 Differentiate from Cellulitis<\/li><li>Reaction Limited to Site of Contact<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Treatment:<ul><li>Avoid Offending Agents<\/li><li>Moisturizers<\/li><li>Consider Topical Corticosteroids \u2013 Debated<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-ff57114\" data-id=\"ff57114\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-896405d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"896405d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-12066 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Erysipelas.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Erysipelas.jpg 500w, https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Erysipelas-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/p><p>Erysipelas <sup>2<\/sup><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b789cbb elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"b789cbb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-12057 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Contact-Dermatitis.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"324\" srcset=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Contact-Dermatitis.jpg 500w, https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Contact-Dermatitis-300x194.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/p><p>Contact Dermatitis from a Buprenorphine Patch <sup>3<\/sup><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-38798f5 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"38798f5\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-740ccba\" data-id=\"740ccba\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-34aea6f elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"34aea6f\" data-eleme